- page_title "Speaking"

h2.mb-6.text-pink-dark
  | Speaking

.copy
  p I relish the chance to share the things that are are making a difference in my life as a software developer: better application architecture and continuing innovation in Ruby.
  p I’d love to do this more. I’m available for speaking opportunities in 2019. Please <a href="/about">get in touch</a>.

h3.mb-6.text-pink-dark
  | Past talks

- talks.each do |talk|
  div.mb-6
    - if talk.url
      a class="inline-block mb-1 font-bold text-base text-black hover:text-pink hover:no-underline" href=talk.url
        | #{talk.title}&nbsp;→
    - else
      div class="mb-1 font-bold text-base text-black"
        = talk.title

    div class="mb-1 text-sm text-black"
      - if talk.event_url
        a class="text-black hover:text-pink" href=talk.event_url = talk.event
      - else
        = talk.event
      | , #{talk.location}

    div class="font-mono text-xs text-grey"
      /datetime=article.datetime_code
      time = talk.date.strftime("%b %Y")

    / div class="font-mono text-xs text-grey"
    /   time datetime=article.datetime_code = article.display_date

    / div class="font-mono text-xs text-grey"
    /   time datetime=article.datetime_code = article.display_date
    /   - if article.external?
    /     '  -
    /     = article.external_url_domain
